        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="30days操作系统day1">30days操作系统day1</h1>
<p>环境：</p>
<p>​	win10  64位专业版</p>
<p>​</p>
<h2 id="试运行">试运行</h2>
<p>​	书上正式开始首先要求能运行这个系统</p>
<p>​	去官网http://hrb.osask.jp/下好所需文件</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AshMOB/md_picture/202204201332583.png" alt="image-20220420133250533" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>​			<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AshMOB/md_picture/202204201333162.png" alt="image-20220420133302133" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>下载这两个文件放到自己喜欢的文件夹</p>
<p>还有随书光盘的内容，网上都能找到，不细说了</p>
<p>按书里说的用16进制编辑器做好初始镜像</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AshMOB/md_picture/202204201334788.png" alt="image-20220420133412720" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AshMOB/md_picture/202204201334724.png" alt="image-20220420133442685" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>​	如图，bat文件的来源和内容书里都写清楚了</p>
<p>win10点cons_nt这个运行</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AshMOB/md_picture/202204201336604.png" alt="image-20220420133611544" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>成功运行</p>
<p>之后是作者教如何利用汇编生成helloos.img，比较详细，不多赘述。</p>
<h1 id="day2">day2</h1>
<p>前部分介绍汇编知识</p>
<p>注意ORG 0x7c00这个标识</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AshMOB/md_picture/202204211311709.png" alt="image-20220421131120624" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>说明该处区域是引导程序的加载区</p>
<p>一些有关makefile的简单介绍</p>
